  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - Notwithstanding the description given on the application form, the local planning authority regard the principal elevation to be that facing Imperial Drive and as such, consider the extension proposed is a rear extension. The proposed single storey rear extension by reason of its rearward projection would not be within the tolerances of Schedule 2, Part 1, Class A, A.1(f)(i) of The Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended) and does not benefit from the provisions and condition set out under Schedule 2, Part 1, Class A, A.1(g)(i) and A.4 of The Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended). ",
    "Reason : 2 -  The proposed porch by reason of its siting within 2 metres of the boundary of the curtilage of the dwellinghouse with a highway would not be within the tolerances of Schedule 2, Part 1, Class D, D.1(d) of The Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended). ",
    "Reason : 3 - The proposal is NOT therefore a lawful development."
  ],
